# v2/data is production-only (FDClient + Price models ship on the VPS,
# not in this repo). Carve out Phase 4.5-mini's price_source.py + its
# smoke test so the yfinance migration is repo-tracked; production's
# __init__.py / client.py / models.py stay untracked.
!v2/data/
v2/data/*
!v2/data/price_source.py
!v2/data/test_price_source.py

